1 - #8-32 Machine Screw Nut
1 - #8-32 Socket Cap Screw, 1-1/2" long
1 - 9/64 drive hex key (#8)
1 - protractor or cellphone with protractor app.
1 - set of bracket and collar the correct angle for your windshield.

Use protractor or cellphone with protractor app to determine ideal mount angle for windshield. Print out file at nearest angle and assemble flat faces together, snap collar around them and insert nut into hex end, bolt into round end, and engage threads on nut. Mount EON and adjust as necessary for yaw, then tension collar by tightening nut to hold Eon position.
